Testing the VI.ggplot() within the BrailleR package"

A. Jonathan R. Godfrey

N.B. the commands here are either exact copies of the commands presented in Wickham (2009) or some minor alterations to them. Notably, some code given in the book no longer works. This is given a #!

The ggplot2 package has a summary method that often but not always offers something to show that things have changed from one plot to another. Iâ€™ve kept the use of this command in as it shows where we need to look for more information and from where we ought to look for it.
